{
  "texts": [
    "This section presents detailed information about human involvement, contributing to the quality of the dataset.",
    "Data construction.",
    "Overall, there are 6 human annotators, including 1 PhD candidate, 3 master students, and 2 senior undergraduates, who are also authors of this paper.",
    "They are all well-trained on the curation principles in Section 3.2.",
    "Majoring in AI, computer science, and cyber security, they are qualified for data curation with proficiency in English, programming, and a basic background in LLM and agents."
  ]
}